data.description: Beautifully landscaped 4 bedroom 2 and a half bath Colonial style home tucked away in Twin Oaks. This home has so much living space that includes a Living Room, Dining Room, Eat-in Kitchen, Family Room, Half Bath and a 4-Season Room on the first floor. The second floor has 4 bedrooms and 2 full baths and an attic fan. The walk out basement features a Gym/Flex Room, a Kitchen area, Rec Room and another Flex Room. There is a Deck overlooking the Scenic Wooded Backyard, with stairs that lead down to a small creek. (H20 tank Oct. '23, Kitchen Updated in '22, Gym '22, Flooring in Family Room, Dining Room and Living Room '18) Call today for showing!
